OL,7,FA patient deemed fit enough by doctors
OL,8,Fto be discharged has been stuck in
OL,9,Fhospital for more than seven years,
OL,10,Faccording to new figures.
OL,12,FNHS Fife confirmed one of its patients
OL,13,Fhas been experiencing delayed
OL,14,Fdischarge for 2,576 days ` the
OL,15,Fequivalent of seven years and 21 days
OL,16,Fin hospital.
