OL,3,CPatient stuck in Scottish hospital for
OL,4,Cmore than seven years awaiting
OL,5,Cdischarge
OL,7,FA series of freedom of information
OL,8,Frequests by the Scottish Conservatives
OL,9,Frevealed many patients are waiting
OL,10,Fyears to leave hospital after being
OL,11,Ftold it is safe to do so. The figure
OL,12,Fis well above the average delayed
OL,13,Fdischarge time for the health board.
OL,15,FThere were also patients in NHS
OL,16,FHighland and NHS Lothian waiting more
OL,17,Fthan four years, while NHS Greater
OL,18,FGlasgow and Clyde ` Scotland's biggest
OL,19,Fhealth board ` has a patient waiting
OL,20,Fmore than 1,334 days.
