OL,3,CPatient stuck in Scottish hospital for
OL,4,Cmore than seven years awaiting
OL,5,Cdischarge
OL,7,FOfficial figures showed that in
OL,8,FNovember alone, patients whose
OL,9,Fdischarge had been delayed spent an
OL,10,Fadditional 60,696 days in hospital,
OL,11,Fwith this 7% higher than the same
OL,12,Fmonth in 2023.
OL,14,FPublic Health Scotland data found that
OL,15,Fin November 2024 there were more than
OL,16,F2,000 people whose discharge was
OL,17,Fdelayed, with many of them likely to
OL,18,Fhave been waiting for care
OL,19,Farrangements to be made.
