OL,7,FThe Scottish Tories said Sunday's
OL,8,Fstatistics "exposed the true scale of
OL,9,Fthe delayed discharge crisis on the
OL,10,FSNP's watch".
OL,12,FDr Sandesh Gulhane, the party's health
OL,13,Fspokesperson, said the figures should
OL,14,Fbe a "source of shame" for successive
OL,15,FSNP health secretaries.
OL,17,FIt comes just days after the Scottish
OL,18,FGovernment announced it had scrapped
OL,19,Flong-held plans for a National Care
OL,20,FService.
