OL,7,FA Scottish government spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "While we cannot comment on
OL,9,Findividual patients, there are some
OL,10,Fhighly complex cases ` including
OL,11,Fmental health patients or hospital-
OL,12,Fbased complex clinical care patients `
OL,13,Fwhere unfortunately it is extremely
OL,14,Fdifficult to find an appropriate care
OL,15,Fpackage.
OL,17,F"Long-term hospital inpatient cases of
OL,18,Fthis nature remain rare, and the
OL,19,Flatest published official statistics
OL,20,Fshows the median length of delay for
OL,21,FNHS Fife was 20 days.
