OL,10,Fwe continue to work closely with our
OL,11,Ffour health and social care partners
OL,12,Fin Lothian to tackle delayed
OL,13,Fdischarges, including increasing
OL,14,Fcommunity health care capacity, home
OL,15,Fcare and care home availability."
